{
  "stem": "311.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this bull with this, achtung-- every time every German comes in, somebody can chop his fingers off, can make a big accident.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, no more.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You don't come in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you come in, as a-- a regularly, it's all right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Lunchtime, yes, after work, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He-- he had a good excuse, safety.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, this was great.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When in Gross-Rosen, when we were set up that we had to be going to Schindler, I think they give us something, a sandwich or something.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, this was the first time in history of Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was like a-- a box lunch or whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But Schindler must have prepared for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a little box.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was a box lunch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a-- it was a sandwich with jam.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was an apple.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It looked good, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you know a feeling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--from one camp to the other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Still, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was half open, you know, the door, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't see any wires out the window, you know, there's the-- It was-- it was a-- you-- you could see it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It-- it start getting a little humane.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Overnight.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Overnight.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came about 9 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and then we saw the factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saw two machines being unloaded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It had 200, 300-ton presses, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to direct from the railroad-- the railroad was like a quarter mile away from the factory.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And to direct a machine, a 300-ton press, and they didn't have the right idea, you know, how to.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were dug in-- in-- in the mud.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if you try to take the ropes and start schlepping and pushing, you know, it doesn't want to.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It digs in deep into the ground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "700.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
